— it's on the second floor, across from the staircase and just to the right of the Undergraduate Commons. If you haven't had the time to stop in quite yet, we'd love to meet you next semester! \n\nGood luck with finals and have a restful winter break!!", 'components': [], 'channel_type': 0, 'channel_id': '1472642931163664465', 'author': {'username': 'zuimuffins', 'public_flags': 0, 'primary_guild': None, 'id': '1420154185780826303', 'global_name': 'Muffins', 'display_name_styles': None, 'discriminator': '0', 'collectibles': None, 'clan': None, 'avatar_decoration_data': None, 'avatar': 'efdb65fc86a18cc65e2fdb7aa87fa545'}, 'attachments': [], 'guild_id': '1471950852020371539'}}
