.dev/)**\n👉 **[View the Full Schedule](https://cheesehacks.dev/)**\n\nLet’s make something "grate" together! 🧀💻', 'components': [], 'channel_type': 0, 'channel_id': '1472642931163664465', 'author': {'username': 'zuimuffins', 'public_flags': 0, 'primary_guild': None, 'id': '1420154185780826303', 'global_name': 'Muffins', 'display_name_styles': None, 'discriminator': '0', 'collectibles': None, 'clan': None, 'avatar_decoration_data': None, 'avatar': 'efdb65fc86a18cc65e2fdb7aa87fa545'}, 'attachments': [], 'guild_id': '1471950852020371539'}}
